Design a TestScores class that has members variables to hold three test scores.

The class should have a constructor, acc3essor, and mutoator functions for the test score fields
and member function that returns the average of the test scores.

Demonstrate the class by writing a seperate program that creates an instanc of the class.

The program should ask the user to enter three test scorees, which are stored in the TestScores object.

Then the program should display the average of the scores, as reported bny the TestScores object.
